nodes.detailed_info: This is a SKOS vocabulary presentation of the time units of the International Chronostratigraphic Chart represented as SKOS Concepts. Beginning and End ages are given for each unit in units of Millions of Years Ago (MYA).

skos:definition.@value: This is a SKOS vocabulary presentation of the time units of the International Chronostratigraphic Chart represented as SKOS Concepts. Beginning and End ages are given for each unit in units of Millions of Years Ago (MYA).

properties.skos:historyNote: This vocabulary uses IRIs created for the Geologic Timescale (2020) data (see http://resource.geosciml.org/vocabulary/timescale/) with dates updated from the 2023-09 Chart (see https://stratigraphy.org/chart)
